\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Intro\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 scarcity \'97 having less than you feel you need\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 scarcity changes us\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 the coins \'91looked\'92 largest to poorer kids when asked to size\'a0\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'91subjective expansion of time\'92 that comes with an increased engagement of attention\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 in economics, scarcity is ubiquitous\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Feeling vs. having scarcity\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
